    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention or could serve as a dedicated parts car. The exterior has extensive damage, including heavy oxidation, deep scratches, and noticeable rust spots on several panels. Mechanically, the engine runs but suffers from a rough idle and visible fluid leaks, and the transmission shifts harshly between gears. The interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics; it is priced strictly as-is to reflect these serious concerns.",
