      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly way to get around? This car is a true diamond in the rough! It has plenty of character and is ready for a dedicated owner who can give it the mechanical and cosmetic TLC it needs. While it shows significant wear and will require some repairs to be road-ready, it\u2019s a fantastic opportunity for someone handy to own a vehicle at a fraction of the cost!",
