    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to be made roadworthy. The engine currently runs roughly and exhibits several fluid leaks, while the transmission shifts are noticeably harsh. Externally, the body shows significant rust on the rocker panels and various dents, and the interior upholstery is heavily worn and torn. This car is best suited as a dedicated project for a mechanic or as a source for parts.",
