    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've honestly got to see this beauty in person\u2014it is an absolute dream! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it that it still looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s spotless inside and out, and it\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019m looking for a new home for this gem, so if you want a ride that feels brand new and is ready for the road, this is the one! Drop me a message if you're interested\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
