      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six and a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This example is mechanically impeccable, boasting a comprehensive service file including a recent VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement, and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The factory limited-slip differential remains tight, and the suspension geometry is perfectly dialed to OEM specifications for maximum feedback. Finished in original paint with a pristine interior, this M3 represents a turnkey opportunity for the purist seeking the peak of the analog driving era.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Garage kept. Original paint. No accidents. Full service history included. Showroom condition.",
      "price": 43000.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in absolute showroom condition, this vehicle is a rare find for the discerning collector. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero paint imperfections or road rash, while the interior remains pristine, featuring supple, unblemished leather and a cockpit that still retains its original factory scent. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized centers, documented in a comprehensive history file that accompanies the car. Garage-kept under a breathable cover and never driven in inclement weather, the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched alloy wheels, every detail reflects a life of meticulous, no-expense-spared care. This car offers a driving experience indistinguishable from the day it left the showroom floor.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
